---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - ThangQT" description="Computer science student at UET-VNU passionate about open-source software and Linux." jsonLdType="person">
  <section class="col-content">
    <h2 style="font-size: var(--fs-body-m); margin-bottom: var(--margin);">About Me</h2>
    
    <p>
      I'm Thang, a computer science student at UET-VNU. While I'm still 
      studying, most of my free time goes into building side projects. 
      It's how I actually learn.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      I love tinkering. There's a certain rush when you break something, 
      the adrenaline when you're debugging at 2am, and the satisfaction 
      when it finally clicks. Building something for yourself, by yourself, 
      is deeply satisfying.
    </p>

    <p>
      I'm drawn to open-source and Linux because I value freedom and control. 
      Being able to shape your tools exactly how you want is the whole point.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: var(--fs-body-m); margin-top: calc(var(--margin) * 2); margin-bottom: var(--margin);">
      Outside of Code
    </h2>
    
    <p>
      Music might be the best thing humanity has ever created. It lets you 
      feel emotions and visit places you never would otherwise. It's my 
      constant companion.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      When I need to take a break, I dive into movies, games, or puzzles. 
      I'm also trying to reclaim my attention span from the internet, relearning to 
      love reading books the way I used to.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: var(--fs-body-m); margin-top: calc(var(--margin) * 2); margin-bottom: var(--margin);">
      Contact
    </h2>

    <p>
      You can reach me directly via email at
      <a href="mailto:thang@thangqt.com">thang@thangqt.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <aside class="col-detail">
    <div class="is-visible">
      <h2>About</h2>
    </div>
  </aside>
</Layout>
